Privacy Policy

Dreamscape Adventures is a casual game designed for fun and entertainment. This game does not collect, store, or share any personal information from players.

No login required: You can play the game anonymously.

No personal data collected: We do not track your name, email, location, or any other personal information.

Advertisements: The game may show ads to support its development. These ads may use anonymized data, but no personal information is collected by the game.
